ActPlant Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending and Repealing Certain Regulations made under the Plant Protection Act (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending and Repealing CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE PLANT PROTECTION ACT (Miscellaneous Program) addresses comments provided by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations (SJCSR) and repeals the Potato Wart Compensation Regulations (SOR/2001-451). The amendments consist of editorial changes and are being made to ensure consistency between the English and French versions of the Regulations.
